    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <urn:reckons:integration/Integrations> ;
    rdfs:label "Indico Events" ;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Import scientific conference programs from Indico (CERN's event management system). Sessions, contributions, and speakers become structured triples." .

